Symbol;mso-ansi-language:EN-GB'><span style=3D'mso-list:Ignore'>&middot;<sp=
an
style=3D'font:7.0pt "Times New Roman"'>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;=
&nbsp;&nbsp;
</span></span></span><![endif]><span lang=3DEN-GB style=3D'mso-ansi-languag=
e:EN-GB'>Racial
research bonuses<o:p></o:p></span></p>

<p class=3DMsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle style=3D'text-indent:-.25in;mso-list:=
